
1  Ber bedo jachan ma timne kare,

moloyo bedo jamoko ma wechene obam.


2  Ng’at maonge gi rieko to gombo gik moko, ok nyal dhi nyime maber.

Jarikni jamuod nyoyo gi kuoyo.


3  Ng’at mofuwo kethore kende owuon,

to bang’e owacho ni Ruoth Nyasaye ema otimone kamano.


4  Jomwandu pile yudo osiepe mang’eny.

Jochan to kata mana osiepe manok ma gin-go ringo weyo.


5  Janeno ma jamriambo ok nyal tony mak okum.

Adier, ng’at ma wacho miriambo lilo ok tony.


6  Ng’ato ka ng’ato temo mondo joma dongo ohere,

kendo ng’ato ka ng’ato wacho ni en osiep ng’ama bade lach.


7  Ka omine jachan duto ochaye,

osiepene to koro dijwang’e machal nadi!

Kata obedo ni otemo matek mondo oyud osiep,

to ok onyal yudo.


8  Ng’at ma dwaro rieko rito ngimane maber,

kendo ng’at maparo gima osepuonjore dhi nyime kare.


9  Janeno mariambo ok nyal tony mak okum.

Ng’at ma kamano nolal nono.


10  Joma ofuwo ok owinjore dag maber.

Wasumbni bende ok owinjore bed gi loch kuom jodong gweng’.


11  Ng’at mariek, iye ok wang’ piyo.

Ka ng’ato otimoni marach,

to en gima ber moloyo ka ifwayo.


12  Ruoth ma mirima omako chalo gi sibuor maruto,

to ka omor kodi, to morneno chalo koth machue.


13  En masira bedo wuon wuowi mofuwo.

Dhako ma ralep bende chalo gi pi maton ma ok chogi.


14  Dala kod mwandu ema wuon nyathi weyone.

Dhako mariek to Ruoth Nyasaye ema chiwo.


15  Nindo mit ni jasamwoyo,

to ng’at makamano kech biro nego.


16  Rit chike Ruoth Nyasaye mondo idag aming’a,

nikech kichayogi to initho.


17  Ka imiyo jachan gimoro,

to ichalo ng’at ma holo Ruoth Nyasaye,

nikech Ruoth Nyasaye nodwoknigo.


18  Ka nyithindi oketho to puonjgi gi chwat

ka pod gitindo ma ginyalo winjoe gimoro.

Ka ok itim kamano to ikethogi.


19  Ng’at ma jamrima nyaka ikre owuon

ni yudo kum ma mirimbe kelo,

nikech ka igole e chandruok makamano dichiel,

to ng’e ni ibiro timo kamano pile.


20  Chik iti ni rieko ming’adoni, kendo yie mondo opuonji,

eka chieng’ moro nibed mariek.


21  Ng’ato nyalo chano gik mathoth,

to dwaro mar Ruoth Nyasaye ema timore.


22  Enn wichkuot bedo jawuoro.

Bedo jachan too ber moloyo bedo jamriambo.


23  Luor Ruoth Nyasaye mondo idag aming’a gi kue

maonge gima thagi.


24  Ng’at ma jasamwoyo luto lwete e tawo,

to tero lwete e dhoge tame.


25  Josunga nyaka kum mondo joma kia gik moko opuonjre.

Ng’at mariek to puonjore apuonja kokwere.


26  Ng’at mamon gi wuon, kendo riembo min e dala,

kelo wichkuot kod achaya.


27  Wuoda, ka iweyo puonjruok,

to piyopiyo nono wiyi biro wil gi gik ma iseng’eyo.


28  Janeno man gi sadha e chunye ketho bura.

Joricho to chadho mana weche mamono.


29  Josunga gi joma ofuwo duto biro yudo kum.

